{"tid":2495354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) SPSS做唔到reliability test","createTime":"2021-04-19T06:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:18:04.000Z","uid":135008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87170f231561f6cec683d4664605108a062db74d","tid":2495354,"uid":135008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"我份問卷可以skip題目, 即係Q1問yes or no, 答yes跳去Q2-3, 答no跳去Q4-5<br />\n我將Q1-5放入spss做reliability test, 結果話There are too few cases (N = 0) for the analysis<br />\n係咪因為有missing value? 但我google話reliability test 會exclude missing value<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/reliability-fails-0-cases-each-case-has-missing-values-design\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibm.com%2Fsupport%2Fpages%2Freliability-fails-0-cases-each-case-has-missing-values-design&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=498076f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/reliability-fails-0-cases-each-case-has-missing-values-design</a><br />\n之後search到上面條link 唔知關唔關事, 但係睇唔明<br />\n我本身好少用spss<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f179bad26d2fd7369ec24ce8aeabdf90dd6c9489","tid":2495354,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"你print screen 睇下點入data先?"},{"pid":"0150af4a7ac7795afd4cffffbbfceaaa1a278e22","tid":2495354,"uid":135008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f179bad26d2fd7369ec24ce8aeabdf90dd6c9489","tid":2495354,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"你print screen 睇下點入data先?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa238